---
title: Buttered-Up Butternut Squash Risotto with Sage and Pepitas
description: Butternut squash is a versatile veg that goes with just about everything, but its ultimate use might just be in risotto. Its sweet flavor and tender flesh provide the perfect contrast to the rich, brothy creaminess of the rice. To really turn up the taste in this recipe, we’re also adding herby sage, shreds of Parmesan, and a pepita garnish for crunch.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/buttered-up-butternut-squash-risotto-fc27e5c1.jpg
